211
00:13:22,160 --> 00:13:23,080
Then step over my dead body first.

212
00:13:48,160 --> 00:13:49,490
Tell me where Nawa is!

213
00:14:21,010 --> 00:14:21,670
Get up here!

214
00:16:29,770 --> 00:16:33,480
I'm sorry, Nawa…
This is as far as I could go…

215
00:16:35,700 --> 00:16:36,550
Nawa.

216
00:17:20,540 --> 00:17:21,560
Nawa.

