224
00:18:28,680 --> 00:18:29,670
What's wrong?

225
00:18:30,810 --> 00:18:31,300
Mr. Phurit!

226
00:18:32,410 --> 00:18:33,280
Can you hear me?

227
00:18:37,970 --> 00:18:38,490
Hey.

228
00:18:41,890 --> 00:18:42,520
Nawa.

229
00:18:45,080 --> 00:18:46,560
I finally found you.

230
00:18:51,130 --> 00:18:52,220
I came for you…

231
00:18:56,830 --> 00:18:58,110
I'm sorry I'm late.

232
00:19:01,170 --> 00:19:02,650
You don't hate me?

233
00:19:16,380 --> 00:19:17,620
