234
00:19:27,120 --> 00:19:29,750
Because… I'm a merman.

235
00:19:33,030 --> 00:19:34,740
I think you're beautiful.

236
00:19:41,250 --> 00:19:42,510
No matter what you are,

237
00:19:44,370 --> 00:19:45,410
I love you.

238
00:19:50,170 --> 00:19:51,830
I want to take care of you forever.

239
00:19:53,660 --> 00:19:55,560
I want to spend my life with you.

240
00:19:56,170 --> 00:19:59,080
♪ No need to tell the world that we love each other. ♪

241
00:19:59,080 --> 00:19:59,530
Mr. Phurit!

242
00:19:59,880 --> 00:20:00,990
Spend my life with you.
