00:20:21,640 --> 00:20:22,670
♪ As long as you're with me, ♪

252
00:20:22,670 --> 00:20:23,570
I love you too.
♪ As long as you're with me, ♪

253
00:20:23,620 --> 00:20:25,540
♪ as long as we love each other. ♪

