Mr. Phurit! What's wrong?

255
00:20:28,190 --> 00:20:29,840
Mr. Phurit! Mr. Phurit!

256
00:20:32,530 --> 00:20:33,680
Stay with me!

257
00:20:34,340 --> 00:20:36,030
Mr. Phurit! Mr. Phurit!

258
00:20:38,250 --> 00:20:40,010
Somebody! Anyone!

259
00:20:40,840 --> 00:20:41,480
Mr. Phurit!

260
00:20:42,270 --> 00:20:42,900
Mr. Phurit!

261
00:20:43,580 --> 00:20:44,970
Stay with me! Mr. Phurit!

262
00:20:45,410 --> 00:20:46,050
Mr. Phurit!

263
00:20:46,770 --> 00:20:48,040
Mr. Phurit! Mr. Phurit!

264
00:20:48,860 --> 00:20:51,350
I heard a human trespassed into mermen territory.

265
00:20:52,050 --> 00:20:53,300
Grandpa Samut, please help Mr. Phurit!

266
00:20:53,740 --> 00:20:55,080
